  "body": "## Description\r\nThe function `get_slashings` that retrieves attester slashings from the operation pool is currently flawed, as it calls `get_slashable_indices_modular` with an incorrect closure.\r\nhttps://github.com/sigp/lighthouse/blob/03443c3e5714ae5478173de4a87f92a1c9577549/eth2/operation_pool/src/lib.rs#L224-L225\r\n\r\n## Steps to resolve\r\nI believe (idea from @michaelsproul ) that the correct closure should be\r\n```rust\r\n|index, validator| validator.is_slashable_at(state.current_epoch()) && !to_be_slashed.contains(&index)\r\n```",
